ISSUES:
1. QC pass rate dropped to 13% — MossTTSDelay 8B generates different
   durations than MossTTSLocal 1.7B. Duration matching criteria may need
   recalibration for the Delay model.
2. Audio quality (audit 7/8) is comparable to baseline (7-8/8).
3. GGUF model loads per synthesis call (~3-4s overhead per segment).
   Future: implement persistent model loading for additional ~1.3x speedup.

RECOMMENDATION:
- GGUF backend delivers significant speedup (2.1x)
- Quality is good (audit 7/8) but QC criteria need calibration
- Ready for Hemersons validation

